body_html:
I have an other strange behavior with Tensorbord with the mnist example. (windows 10 Anaconda used)
(worked from out a jupyternotebook) and delivered files at
d:/tmp/tensorflow/mnist/logs/mnist_with_summaries
containing two subdirectorie test and train
then using out of a BAT file:
D:/Anaconda3/Scripts/tensorboard.exe --logdir="d:/tmp/tensorflow/mnist/logs/mnist_with_summaries" --port=6007
THIS works as suspected at: localhost:6007
D:/Anaconda3/Scripts/tensorboard.exe --logdir="d:/tmp/tensorflow/mnist/logs/mnist_with_summaries" --port=6006
Does not show anything using localhost:6006

????
